---
title: Fuss-Free Coconut Chicken Curry & Garlic Rice with Carrot-Cucumber Salsa & Coriander
description: This easy unforgettable Indian chicken curry gets the royal treatment with simmered spices, aromatic garlic rice and a finish of creamy coconut sauce. Who knew something that takes so little effort could be so tasty?

